title: Rigmar Audio Collection 006
description:
Please view Torrent files for the track listings.   Click top left on the BLUE 100 link.   Files are named and tagged for easy import into professional DJ and Club playout software.

Rigmar has been collecting and buying music since 1957 and the rare hard to get or simply too old to be played anymore tracks will be featured in this vast collection, NOT the current easy to get stuff which is mostly all that is seen for download these days online.

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
